<title>SOUTH AFRICA: Tigon in talks, advises caution.</title>
<headline>Tigon in talks, advises caution.</headline>
<dateline>JOHANNESBURG 1997-04-01</dateline>
<text>
<p>Tigon Ltd said on Tuesday it was involved in negotiations which if concluded could have an effect on its share price.</p>
<p>It advised shareholders to exercise caution in their share dealings until a further notice was made.</p>
<p>-- Johannesburg newsroom +27 11 482 1003</p>
